      <title>黑天鹅对冲基金称美联储降息将预示市场崩盘</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/black-swan-hedge-fund-says-fed-rate-cuts-will-signal-market-crash-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国金融市场对降息时机争论不休，但一家尾部风险对冲基金警告称，投资者应充分利用近期经济乐观情绪，因为转向较低利率将预示着市场将发生剧烈崩盘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/black-swan-hedge-fund-says-fed-rate-cuts-will-signal-market-crash-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 15:02:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
